WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.133
Ha, ha, that's only 30 million.

2
00:00:03.133 --> 00:00:05.600
Let your Lin Mengdi's soul be bought

3
00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.233
A mere 30 million

4
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:09.866
Your life is worth more than a fraction of this necklace

5
00:00:09.866 --> 00:00:11.066
Still talking big here

6
00:00:11.066 --> 00:00:12.900
I said you don't deserve me

7
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.633
I am Lin Mengdi's man

8
00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:16.466
It can never be like you

9
00:00:16.466 --> 00:00:18.200
The burden of not seeing hope

10
00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:19.700
OK

11
00:00:23.666 --> 00:00:26.400
Hope you don't regret it

12
00:00:30.933 --> 00:00:33.133
Go to your bed

13
00:00:33.133 --> 00:00:36.200
I want to harvest the traces he left

14
00:00:36.733 --> 00:00:38.666
Let you just remember?

15
00:00:39.133 --> 00:00:41.266
What's the hurry?

16
00:00:42.533 --> 00:00:44.300
Want to get it so easily

17
00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:47.533
Hey, I got you a present

18
00:00:47.533 --> 00:00:48.700
Do you want it or not?

19
00:00:48.900 --> 00:00:50.300
Diamond luxury car

20
00:00:50.300 --> 00:00:53.566
I have no shortage of Golden Dragon Awards for Best Actress

21
00:00:55.766 --> 00:00:57.266
I can get it for you.

22
00:00:57.766 --> 00:01:00.233
I knew you were the one who loved me the most

23
00:01:00.266 --> 00:01:01.933
You are much better than that flying dance

24
00:01:01.933 --> 00:01:04.166
Let's see what true love is

